%%{init: {'theme':'dark', 'themeVariables': {'fontFamily':'monospace','fontSize':'15px'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant X as REXPrimary<br/>(Sepolia)
    participant H as Hyperlane<br/>Bridge
    participant E as PruvExecutor<br/>(PRUV)
    participant K as Keeper /<br/>Monitor

    X->>H: transferRemote(NET USDC) -> msgId
    Note over X: epoch = in-flight, lưu msgId (idempotent)

    alt Relay thành công
        H-->>E: giao USDC
        E->>H: bridge wRWA về -> msgId2
        H-->>X: giao wRWA
        K->>X: settleEpoch()
    else Relay kẹt / timeout
        K->>H: theo dõi msgId - chưa delivered
        Note over K: cảnh báo, KHÔNG settle (chống double theo msgId)
        K->>H: retry delivery
        alt Recover được
            H-->>E: giao USDC (muộn)
            E->>H: bridge wRWA về
            H-->>X: giao wRWA
            K->>X: settleEpoch()
        else Không recover
            K->>E: admin sweep/recover fund kẹt
            Note over X,E: không double-mint, không double-pay
        end
    end
